title: Quid Pro Intro
description:
Welcome to the first episode of the Legally Judgy podcast. Meet the women behind the robes, the brains behind the beauty, and the comics behind the laughs as we dive into their sordid pasts and journeys to the mic. Don’t say we didn’t warn you...
